					input.sheet-checkbox.sheet-ExpToggle(type='checkbox', name='attr_Toggle-Spellslinger-Restrictions-Unused', value='1', checked='')
					span.sheet-anglebox
					span.sheet-ExpHeader
						span(data-i18n='unused') Unused
					.sheet-move
						input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Moves-Spellslinger1A', value='1', checked='')
						span.sheet-mainbox
						span.sheet-grayable
							span(data-i18n='spellslinger-fixed-move1.1')
								i Consumables
								| : You need certain supplies - powders, oils, etc - on hand, some will be used up each cast. If you don&apos;t have them, when you cast, take 1 harm, ignore-armour.
					.sheet-move
						input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Moves-Spellslinger1B', value='1', checked='')
						span.sheet-mainbox
						span.sheet-grayable
							span(data-i18n='spellslinger-fixed-move1.2')
								i Foci
								| : You need wands, staves, and other obvious props to focus. If you don&apos;t have what you need, your combat magic does 1 harm less.
					.sheet-move
						input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Moves-Spellslinger1C', value='1', checked='')
						span.sheet-mainbox
						span.sheet-grayable
							span(data-i18n='spellslinger-fixed-move1.3')
								i Gestures
								| : You need to wave your hands around to use combat magic. If you&apos;re restrained, take -1 ongoing for combat magic.
					.sheet-move
						input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Moves-Spellslinger1D', value='1', checked='')
						span.sheet-mainbox
						span.sheet-grayable
							span(data-i18n='spellslinger-fixed-move1.4')
								i Incantations
								| : You must speak in an arcane language to control your magic. If you use combat magic without speaking, 
								i act under pressure
								|  to avoid scrambling your thoughts.
